review: Ma'am is a great doctor, explained the issue very well and then did a perfect laparoscopy for investigation and the correct deduction of the issue. She is very clear from the beginning and values your time by guiding you in the right direction. Would absolutely recommend her.
Doctor was kind. Explained what could be the problem that I was facing! Would recommend you have a visit if facing any problems.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review: *** ****** ****** ****** **** ***** For an online appointment one would expect distance to not be a problem however the doctor suggested to visit a nearby doctor instead with very little interest in the problem.
reply_text: Visit a nearby doctor as an emergency since the problem is long standing and it needs to be investigated and may require an operative intervention. I would rather guide her to a safe n definitive option than a temporary and ineffective one.

review: No update on appointment.  Should be more friendly. Very fast while explaining issues and how to take medication. Was little arrogant and angry when asked again on how to take medicines.
reply_text: The clinic is open for clearing ur doubts.

tags: Treatment satisfaction,Explanation of the health issue,Doctor friendliness,
review: She is very cooperative and give very satisfactory consultation. She always gives a very good smile. Discusses about the things in detail.
A very good experience. Caring and a understanding doctor. Handles the patients very well n gives them an apt treatment. Overall a very satisfying solution to the problems..

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Wait time,
review: Dr Madhushree is very pleasant and caring and provides detailed explanation for treatment recommended. she instills so much confidence in her patients..Thank you Doctor!!
One of few doctors I visited who had absolutely no unsolicited advice or judgement against my current body weight. Highly recommended for women who maybe shy of visiting docs due to body image issues
Thank you so much for helping me out during these very difficult times. Thank you so much Dr. for solving my problem.
*** ** * **** **** *** thank you so much Mam for Clearing all my problems. She is a very friendly. Thank you
